an operating temperature of at least 5000 C or more, which would be in the form of direct em radiation.Silicon would melt<br>
inside such an engine. Also nuetron radiation over time would make the silicon weak and fragile over time even if it could withstood the heat, until it would break from the force of <br>
its own thermal vibrations.<br>
